  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1403940/extras/2b2f3cdea9d8d12eb065a08fa7d3cc1a.poster.avif?t=1763071007\" width=1170 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1403940/extras/2b2f3cdea9d8d12eb065a08fa7d3cc1a.webm?t=1763071007\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1403940/extras/2b2f3cdea9d8d12eb065a08fa7d3cc1a.mp4?t=1763071007\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >GRIM is an exclusive VR multiplayer survival game where you must survive, stranded on a secluded part of Earth. Survival is not just a choice, but a grueling battle against nature and other players. You must gather resources, craft, and build your base, all to stay alive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1403940/extras/4ab996692dae722dcf3dcc8c4b92c957.poster.avif?t=1763071007\" width=1170 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1403940/extras/4ab996692dae722dcf3dcc8c4b92c957.webm?t=1763071007\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1403940/extras/4ab996692dae722dcf3dcc8c4b92c957.mp4?t=1763071007\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are no rules other than fending for yourself or with friends. Craft tools, armor, and weapons to make your rightful place against rival survivors and the entities that roam it. You can cooperate with friends and neighbors to build settlements. You can trade with players in peace, or raid their bases with menacing intent to steal their riches.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1403940/extras/a87b23e7be3739270f24a1c38da91f5e.poster.avif?t=1763071007\" width=1170 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1403940/extras/a87b23e7be3739270f24a1c38da91f5e.webm?t=1763071007\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1403940/extras/a87b23e7be3739270f24a1c38da91f5e.mp4?t=1763071007\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Constructing your base is entirely under your control, from fortification to mischievous traps. You can craft your base by yourself or with our survivors. Gather your resources and command your territory.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1403940/extras/86476d7513d443b66db0f9365588e50b.poster.avif?t=1763071007\" width=1170 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1403940/extras/86476d7513d443b66db0f9365588e50b.webm?t=1763071007\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1403940/extras/86476d7513d443b66db0f9365588e50b.mp4?t=1763071007\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >GRIM is packed with features for unlimited replay-ability, including:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Simultaneous PVP and PVE - Avoid both players, wildlife and AI.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Scavenge the land and opposing bases for resources, food, water, firearms, and ammunition.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build and Fortify your base</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Team up or go alone on Earth.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find monuments for their outstanding loot.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Craft your tools and build your workshop.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Variety of makeshift weapons ranging from hatchets to assault rifles.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Raid your enemies.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1403940/extras/2b2f3cdea9d8d12eb065a08fa7d3cc1a.poster.avif?t=1763071007\" width=1170 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1403940/extras/2b2f3cdea9d8d12eb065a08fa7d3cc1a.webm?t=1763071007\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1403940/extras/2b2f3cdea9d8d12eb065a08fa7d3cc1a.mp4?t=1763071007\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >GRIM is an exclusive VR multiplayer survival game where you must survive, stranded on a secluded part of Earth. Survival is not just a choice, but a grueling battle against nature and other players. You must gather resources, craft, and build your base, all to stay alive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1403940/extras/4ab996692dae722dcf3dcc8c4b92c957.poster.avif?t=1763071007\" width=1170 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1403940/extras/4ab996692dae722dcf3dcc8c4b92c957.webm?t=1763071007\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1403940/extras/4ab996692dae722dcf3dcc8c4b92c957.mp4?t=1763071007\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are no rules other than fending for yourself or with friends. Craft tools, armor, and weapons to make your rightful place against rival survivors and the entities that roam it. You can cooperate with friends and neighbors to build settlements. You can trade with players in peace, or raid their bases with menacing intent to steal their riches.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1403940/extras/a87b23e7be3739270f24a1c38da91f5e.poster.avif?t=1763071007\" width=1170 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1403940/extras/a87b23e7be3739270f24a1c38da91f5e.webm?t=1763071007\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1403940/extras/a87b23e7be3739270f24a1c38da91f5e.mp4?t=1763071007\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Constructing your base is entirely under your control, from fortification to mischievous traps. You can craft your base by yourself or with our survivors. Gather your resources and command your territory.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1403940/extras/86476d7513d443b66db0f9365588e50b.poster.avif?t=1763071007\" width=1170 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1403940/extras/86476d7513d443b66db0f9365588e50b.webm?t=1763071007\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1403940/extras/86476d7513d443b66db0f9365588e50b.mp4?t=1763071007\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >GRIM is packed with features for unlimited replay-ability, including:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Simultaneous PVP and PVE - Avoid both players, wildlife and AI.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Scavenge the land and opposing bases for resources, food, water, firearms, and ammunition.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build and Fortify your base</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Team up or go alone on Earth.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find monuments for their outstanding loot.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Craft your tools and build your workshop.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Variety of makeshift weapons ranging from hatchets to assault rifles.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Raid your enemies.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
